title: User query: Plan description from client LLM
log: Create a plan that outputs all creditors that do not have "SLETTET" in their name, and that have an id between 193000 and 194000. Output in textfile.

log.thoughts: Plan loads creditors, filters out those with 'SLETTET' in name and with id in the specified range, then outputs the resulting creditor id and name to a text file.

Wayang: Wayang plan sent to Wayang
Err: Wayang error. Plan executed unsucessful
